    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of mid-century elegance. This vintage roadster isn't just a car; it\u2019s a portal to a golden era of motoring. Bathed in a deep, lustrous finish that catches the twilight like liquid silk, every curve tells a story of sun-drenched coastal drives and moonlit escapes. Inside, the rich, buttery leather carries the faint, nostalgic scent of adventure, while the chrome accents sparkle with the brilliance of a preserved treasure. To drive it is to command a symphony of precision and soul\u2014a rare chance to own not just a vehicle, but a piece of kinetic art that has been kept in a state of absolute grace.",
      "price": 48500.0,
